data.description: Don't miss your opportunity to see this spectacular 4 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath home located in Sneads Ferry! Great space for entertaining with the bedrooms located upstairs.  A huge backyard along with a nice deck and located in a great community.  In addition, you can enjoy your evenings out on the covered front porch and relax. This home is about 15 minutes from Camp Lejeune, and less than an hour from Wilmington, and beaches around you in all directions.
